translated: Leander, Nils Gösta Vilhelm, lawyer, Norrköping, born on 6/3/02 in Hälsingborg to factory worker Wilhelm L. and Elin Dahlgren. Married to Elsa Almqvist. Children: Ulla Britta, born in 1935, Lars Gustaf, born in 1941. Completed student exam in Norrköping in 1921, Bachelor of Arts in Stockholm in 1924, Bachelor of Laws there in 1928. Note: employed in Bråbygden and Finspångaläns district court from 1929-1931, assistant lawyer at Oscar Jenriks Law Firm in Norrköping from 1931-1933, owned own law firm in Linköping from 1933-1935, co-owner of Ernst Söderqvist Law Firm in Norrköping since 1935. Member of the Swedish Bar Association.
